cwe_description: The product dereferences a pointer that it has not confirmed to be valid, which can lead to a crash or exit.
explanation: The code dereferences input pointers a_indices, a_values, a_shape, and b without prior null checks. If any of these pointers are null, it will lead to a null pointer dereference, causing a program crash or denial of service.
